# --- TABLA DE FRECUENCIAS Y CHI-CUADRADO ---
tabla_fuel <- datos %>%
  filter(!is.na(Access.Code)) %>%
  count(Access.Code, name = "Frecuencia") %>%
  mutate(
    Porcentaje = Frecuencia / sum(Frecuencia),
    Esperada = sum(Frecuencia) / n(),
    Chi2_Parcial = (Frecuencia - Esperada)^2 / Esperada,
    Probabilidad_Esperada = Esperada / sum(Frecuencia),
    Etiqueta = paste0(Access.Code, " (", percent(Porcentaje, accuracy = 0.1), ")")
  )

# --- PRUEBA CHI-CUADRADO DE PEARSON ---
chi_test <- chisq.test(tabla_fuel$Frecuencia)
estadistico_chi2 <- chi_test$statistic
gl_chi2 <- chi_test$parameter
pvalor_chi2 <- chi_test$p.value
valor_critico <- qchisq(0.95, df = gl_chi2)

# --- Actualizar columna de interpretacin con valor crtico ---
tabla_fuel <- tabla_fuel %>%
  mutate(
    Interpreta = ifelse(estadistico_chi2 <= valor_critico, "Aprueba", "No aprueba")
  )

# --- GRFICO FRECUENCIA ABSOLUTA ---
ggplot(tabla_fuel, aes(x = reorder(Access.Code, -Frecuencia), y = Frecuencia, fill = Frecuencia)) +
  geom_bar(stat = "identity", width = 0.8) +
  geom_text(aes(label = Frecuencia), vjust = -0.5, size = 3.5) +
  scale_fill_gradient(low = "skyblue", high = "darkblue") +
  labs(
    title = "2.1 Frecuencia Absoluta de Access.Code",
    x = "Codigo de acceso", y = "Frecuencia Absoluta"
  ) +
  theme_minimal() +
  theme(
    plot.title = element_text(hjust = 0.5, face = "bold"),
    axis.text.x = element_text(angle = 45, hjust = 1),
    panel.grid = element_blank(), axis.line = element_line(color = "black")
  )

# --- GRFICO FRECUENCIA RELATIVA ---
n_colores <- nrow(tabla_fuel)
colores_gradiente <- colorRampPalette(c("skyblue", "darkblue"))(n_colores)

ggplot(tabla_fuel, aes(x = reorder(Access.Code, -Porcentaje), y = Porcentaje, fill = Porcentaje)) +
  geom_bar(stat = "identity", width = 0.8) +
  geom_text(aes(label = percent(Porcentaje, accuracy = 0.1)), vjust = -0.5, size = 3.5) +
  scale_fill_gradientn(colors = colores_gradiente) +
  scale_y_continuous(labels = percent_format(accuracy = 1)) +
  labs(
    title = "2.2 Frecuencia Relativa de Access.Code",
    x = "Codigo de acceso", y = "Frecuencia Relativa"
  ) 

  theme_minimal() +
  theme(
    plot.title = element_text(hjust = 0.5, face = "bold"),
    axis.text.x = element_text(angle = 45, hjust = 1),
    panel.grid = element_blank(), axis.line = element_line(color = "black")
  )

# --- GRFICO PROBABILIDAD ESPERADA ---
ggplot(tabla_fuel, aes(x = reorder(Access.Code, -Probabilidad_Esperada), y = Probabilidad_Esperada, fill = Probabilidad_Esperada)) +
  geom_bar(stat = "identity", width = 0.8) +
  geom_text(aes(label = percent(Probabilidad_Esperada, accuracy = 0.1)), vjust = -0.5, size = 3.5) +
  scale_fill_gradient(low = "skyblue", high = "darkblue") +
  scale_y_continuous(labels = percent_format(accuracy = 1)) +
  labs(
    title = "2.3 Probabilidad Esperada por Chi-cuadrado",
    x = "Codigo de acceso", y = "Probabilidad Esperada"
  ) +
  theme_minimal() +
  theme(
    plot.title = element_text(hjust = 0.5, face = "bold"),
    axis.text.x = element_text(angle = 45, hjust = 1),
    panel.grid = element_blank(), axis.line = element_line(color = "black")
  )

# --- GRFICO COMPARACIN OBSERVADO VS ESPERADO ---
ggplot(tabla_fuel, aes(x = reorder(Access.Code, -Frecuencia))) +
  geom_bar(aes(y = Frecuencia, fill = "Observado"), stat = "identity", position = position_nudge(x = -0.2), width = 0.4) +
  geom_bar(aes(y = Esperada, fill = "Esperado"), stat = "identity", position = position_nudge(x = 0.2), width = 0.4) +
  scale_fill_manual(name = "Distribucin", values = c("Observado" = "skyblue", "Esperado" = "darkblue")) +
  labs(
    title = "2.4 Comparacin de Frecuencia Observada vs Esperada",
    x = "Codigo de acceso", y = "Frecuencia"
  ) +
  theme_minimal() +
  theme(
    plot.title = element_text(hjust = 0.5, face = "bold"),
    legend.position = "top",
    axis.text.x = element_text(angle = 45, hjust = 1),
    panel.grid = element_blank(), axis.line = element_line(color = "black")
  )

# --- GRFICO CORRELACIN DE CHI-CUADRADO PARCIAL (DISPOSICIN HORIZONTAL) ---
ggplot(tabla_fuel, aes(x = Chi2_Parcial, y = Esperada)) +
  geom_point(size = 3, color = "skyblue") +
  geom_line(color = "darkblue", linewidth = 0.8) +  # Lnea que conecta los puntos en orden
  geom_smooth(method = "lm", se = FALSE, linetype = "dashed", color = "darkblue") +
  labs(
    title = "2.5 Correlacin: Chi Parcial vs Esperado",
    x = "Contribucin Chi", y = "Frecuencia Esperada"
  ) +
  theme_minimal() +
  theme(
    plot.title = element_text(hjust = 0.5, face = "bold"),
    panel.grid = element_blank(), 
    axis.line = element_line(color = "black")
  )

    style = 'caption-side: top; text-align: center; font-size:18px; font-weight: bold; font-family: Segoe UI; padding: 10px;',
    paste0("2.6 Chi-cuadrado Access.Code  X = ", round(estadistico_chi2, 2),
           ", gl = ", gl_chi2, ", valor crtico = ", round(valor_critico, 2),
           ", p  ", format.pval(pvalor_chi2, digits = 3),
           ifelse(estadistico_chi2 <= valor_critico, "  Modelo ACEPTADO ( = 0.05)", "  Modelo RECHAZADO ( = 0.05)"))
  ),

  rownames = FALSE
)
